
Welcome to the Money Brokers Association.
 
 More than 1 customer served. 
 We can guarantee the highest security for your money.
 There's just one robbery a day.

 What do we offer ?

 To open an account, type 'account'.
 
 Check your statement by typing 'statement'. 

 If you are in need of your money  (you always are, aren't you ?) you might
 want to 'withdraw' it.

 Last but not least, 'deposit' the amount you've earned after a hard day
 of adventuring.

